#!/usr/bin/env python
"""
Complete Facebook Scraper
Combines all scraping functionality in one script:
- Posts scraping
- Images scraping
- Complete comment scraping (all comments and replies)
- Manual login support
- Smart detection of posts with comments

This script uses the SmartFacebookScraper from facebook_scraper_smart.py for enhanced comment extraction.
"""

